	(text "ADL5801 has 50 ohm network suggestion in its datasheet.\nHowever ADL5802 specifically states that it needs 200ohm diff\nTherefore i will use 100ohm pullup and will not use and transformers\nsince the if will be below 10MHz or so."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 214.63 29.718 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.524 1.524)
			)
		)
		(uuid "5e57235c-9a1f-4f77-9a48-a4b47b1a1efc")
	)
	(text "IMPORTANT: BALUN is 50:50 so output is differential 50 ohm.\nAlso ADL5802 expects 50 ohm differential as well.\nTherefore rf trace width spacing changes at that part!!!"
